===== Helpers & Collections =====


=== Helpers ===
- Arrays:
    = array_first
    = aray_get // with nested arrays using dot notation
    = array_has
    = array_pluck // makes an array of one column of the whole array
    = array_random

- Strings:
    = e // htmlentities
    = starts_with
    = ends_with
    = str_contains
    = str_limit
    = str_is
    = str_random
    = str_slug
    = str_plural
    = __ // translation

- Application Paths
    = app_path
    = base_path
    = config_path
    = database_path
    = storage_path

- URLs
    = action // points to a controller, third parameter [true, false] => [absolute, relative]
    = url, secure_url
    = url => current, full, previous
    = mix

- Miscellaneos
    = abort
    = abort_unless
    = abort_if
    = auth
    = back
    = collect
    = config
    = csrf_field, csrf_token
    = dd
    = env // don't use env outside config files
    = dispatch
    = factory
    = old
    = redirect
    = response
    = view

=== Collections ===
- toArray // converts any collection or eloquent
- all // converts only collections
- filter, reject
- where
- first, last
- each
- map
- reduce
- pluck
- chunk, take
- groupBy
- reverse, shuffle
- sort
- sortBy
- sortByDesc
- count
- isEmpty
- isNotEmpty
- avg
- sum


